With an understanding of the importance in healthy living and community bonding, SHAKARASQUARE.COM in collaboration with ONTOGENY MEDIA presents the third (3rd) edition of the annual FESTAC FITNESS WALK with the aim of raising awareness on healthy living, community bonding, environmental development and social networking among participants. This years edition is sponsored by Power Oil. As a company that sensitises the public on the importance of engaging in body fitness activities with their ‘PAY WITH CALORIES’ Initiatives; there is no better company to partners with, the organisers said. To be anchored by MC PROF with a special guest appearance by Nollywood superstar Bolanle Ninalowo AKA Nino, the 5km “mobile” fun-filled inspiring Saturday morning walk scheduled for the 20th of April 2019 from 7.00am – 10am will have high-end individuals, celebrities and the general Festac public walk in their thousands along major roads around the Festac metropolis to the ending point at Festival Mall under maximum security in meeting the projects objectives, create an on the spot solution to a community challenge and entertain participants all under the glare of media.